A|date=January 2018|accessdate=4 February 2018}} ''Click on the link Neuzulassungen von Personenkraftwagen nach Marken und Modellreihen im Dezember 2017 (FZ 10) (XLS, 153 KB, Datei ist nicht barrierefrei) to download the file with registrations figures.''</ref><ref name=\"SalesGer2018\">{{cite web | url=https://www.kba.de/DE/Statistik/Fahrzeuge/Neuzulassungen/MonatlicheNeuzulassungen/2018/201812_GV1monatlich/201812_node.html | title= Neuzulassungen von Personenkraftwagen nach Segmenten und Modellreihen im Dezember 2018 (FZ 11) (xlsx, 75 KB, Datei ist nicht barrierefrei) |language=German |trans-title=New registrations of passenger cars by segments and models in December 2018| author=Kraftfahrt-Bundesamt (KBA)|publisher=KBA|date=January 2019 |accessdate=14 January 2019}} ''Click on the link Neuzulassungen von Personenkraftwagen nach Marken und Modellreihen im Dezember 2018 (FZ 11) (xlsx, 75 KB, Datei ist nicht barrierefrei) to download the file with registrations figures by model.''</ref>\n| 17,340\n| 5,095\n| 4,319\n| 2,863\n| 2,271\n| 2,233\n| 559\n\n|-\n| align=left | {{UK}}<ref name=\"UK3Q2017\">{{cite web | url=http://www.racfoundation.org/data/plug-in-grant-eligible-vehicles-licensed-by-quarter | title=Plug-in grant eligible vehicles licensed (at the end of Q3 2017) | author = RAC Foundation | publisher=[[RAC Foundation]]| location=UK | date=January 2018 | accessdate=6 February 2018}} ''This figure corresponds to eligible vehicles for the plug-in car and van grant schemes as licensed in the UK at the end of Q2 2017 (not cumulative sales).''</ref><ref name=\"UKcum2Q2015\">{{cite web|url=http://www.racfoundation.org/media-centre/ultra-green-cars-on-the-road-Q2-2015-180915|title=Ultra-green cars \u2013 latest on-the-road figures|author=RAC Foundation|publisher=RAC Foundation|date=18 September 2015|accessdate=4 October 2015|author-link=RAC Foundation}} ''A total of 1,534 BMW i3 were registered in the UK since 2013 through December 2014.''</ref><ref name=\"UK2014_2015\">{{cite news|url=http://www.fleetnews.co.uk/news/manufacturer-news/2016/01/15/record-breaking-year-for-plug-in-cars |title=Record-breaking year for plug-in cars |author=Staff |work=Fleet News |date=15 January 2016|accessdate=17 January 2016}} ''A total of 1,393 BMW i3s were registered in the UK in 2014, and 2,213 in 2015.''</ref>\n| 8,365{{efn|name=UK|Number of vehicles as licensed in the UK at the end of Q2 2017 (not cumulative sales).}}\n|\n| {{efn|name=NA|Sales/registration figures not available}}\n| {{efn|name=NA|Sales/registration figures not available}}\n| 2,213\n| 1,393\n| 141 <!--as per the sources provided 1,534 (cum Dec 2014) - 1,393 (2014 registrations) = 141 (registrations in 2013)-->\n\n|-\n| align=left | {{FRA}}<ref name=\"SalesFR2010_14\">{{cite web|url=http://www.automobile-propre.com/dossiers/voitures-electriques/chiffres-vente-immatriculations-france/|title=Chiffres de vente & immatriculations de voitures \u00e9lectriques en France|trans-title=Sales figures & electric car registrations in France|author=Automobile Propre|publisher=Automobile Propre|accessdate=1 February 2015|language=French}} ''See \"Ventes de voitures \u00e9lectriques\" for 2013 registrations. REx variant registrations are not included.''</ref><ref name=\"FRASales2014\">{{cite web |url=http://www.avere-france.org/Site/Article/?article_id=5954 |title=Le march\u00e9 du v\u00e9hicule \u00e9lectrique maintient sa progression en 2014 |language=French |trans-title=The electric vehicle market continues to grow in 2014 |publisher=AVERE France |author=AVERE-France |date=5 January 2015 |accessdate=28 February 2016}} ''See graph with top 5 models in 2014: A total of 607 i3s were registered in France during 2014 including REx models.''</ref><ref name=\"France2015BEV\">{{cite web | url=http://www.avem.fr/actualite-immatriculations-des-voitures-electriques-62-1-en-2015-5923.html | title= Immatriculations des voitures \u00e9lectriques : + 62,1% en 2015|language=French | trans-title= Registrati