eden2016_2017\">{{cite web |url=http://www.bilsweden.se/statistik/nyregistreringar_per_manad_1/nyregistreringar-2017/definitiva-nyregistreringar-under-2017 |title=Definitiva nyregistreringar under 2017 |language=Swedish|trans-title=Definitive new registrations in 2017 |author=Bil Sweden |publisher=Bil Sweden |date=8 January 2018 |accessdate=31 January 2018}} ''Download the pdf file \"PressRel1712_DEF.pdf\" See table \"Nyregistrerade supermilj\u00f6bilar december 2017\" \u2013 A total of 500 units of both variants were sold in 2016 and 545 in 2017.''</ref><ref name=Sweden2016_2018>{{cite web |url=http://www.bilsweden.se/statistik/arkiv-nyregisteringar-per-manad/arkiv-nyregistrering-per-manad-2018/nyregistreringar-december-2018-(def) |title=Nyregistreringar december 2018 (def) |language=Swedish|trans-title=Definitive new registrations December 2018 (final) |author=Bil Sweden |publisher=Bil Sweden |date=7 January 2019 |accessdate=2 February 2019}} ''Download the pdf file \"PressRel1812_DEF.pdf\" See table: \"Nyregistrerade laddbara personbilar december 2018\"''</ref>\n| 2,405\n| 760\n| 545\n| 500\n| 379\n| 210\n| 11\n\n|-\n| align=left | {{ESP}}<ref name=\"Spain2013\">{{cite web |url=http://aniacam.com/datos/2013/12dic2013.php |language=Spanish|title=Datos de Mercado: Diciembre 2013 \u2013 Matriculaciones de autom\u00f3viles |trans-title=Market data: December 2013 \u2013 Automobiles registrations |authors= Asociaci\u00f3n Nacional de Importadores de Autom\u00f3viles, Camiones, Autobuses y Motocicletas (ANIACAM) |publisher=ANIACAM |date=3 January 2014 |accessdate=3 January 2014}}''Download the file DossierAutom\u00f3viles_diciembre13.xls (929KB)* with current month and cumulative sales for 2013. ''</ref><ref name=\"Spain2014\">{{cite web |url=http://aniacam.com/datos/2014/12dic2014.php |language=Spanish |title=Datos de Mercado: Diciembre 2014 \u2013 Matriculaciones |trans-title=Market data: December 2014 \u2013 Registrations |authors= Asociaci\u00f3n Nacional de Importa