ry of the Lyceum-Northwestern University] ''Lyceum-Northwestern University website'' Accessed 19 April 2020</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | West Visayas State University College of Medicine\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1975\n| [[West Visayas State University]]\n| [[Iloilo]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=WVSMed>[https://wvsu.edu.ph/history/ History] ''West Visayas State University website'' Accessed 19 April 2020</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Virgen Milagrosa University Foundation College of Medicine\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1975\n| [[Virgen Milagrosa University Foundation]]\n| [[Pangasinan]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=VMUMed>[http://www.vmuf.edu.ph/# Virgen Milagrosa University Foundation College of Medicine] ''Virgen Milagrosa University Foundation College of Medicine website'' Accessed 19 April 2020</ref>\n|}\n\n==Oldest normal schools==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Current name\n! scope=\"col\" | Year<br />founded\n! scope=\"col\" | Name at time of&nbsp;foundation\n! scope=\"col\" | Location upon foundation\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{abbr|Ref|Reference}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Universidad de Sta. Isabel]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1875\n| Escuela Normal de Maestras of Colegio de Sta. Isabel\n| Camarines Sur\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=usinaga>[https://www.usi.edu.ph/Inside%20USI/USIONE_History.html Milestones in the History of One USI] ''Universidad de Sta. Isabel website'' Accessed 19 April 2020</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Philippine Normal University]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1901\n| Philippine Normal School\n| Manila\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=pnumanila>[https://www.pnu.edu.ph/about-pnu/history-and-milestone/ History and Milestone A Brief History of the Philippine Normal University] ''Philippine Normal University website'' Accessed 19 April 2020</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[West Visayas State University]